Wishing you a happy new year ❤️ If you’d like some support on how to orient to this next year in a way that feels energizing, aligned, and inspiring, my “Life Makeover” Masterclass (previously named, “New Year, True You”) is 50% off until Tuesday. Link is in my bio.

A few things it covers:

>Building a life from wholeness instead of deficit;
>Connecting to your inner compass;
>Focusing on developing good systems instead of goals;
>Taking bold action in the face of fear;
>Using imagination and envisioning to create a life of alignment;
>Manifesting/Creating from “feeling” instead of “ideas”;
>A 10-Minute Intuition Practice;
> 3 Steps for Accessing Intuitive Knowing
> Supplemental Meditations

This masterclass also includes ample follow-up resources such as book recommendations, practices, tips, a written overview of our session, and strategies to take with you to create a beautiful year.

You will also receive LIFE-LONG access to the masterclass recording and resources.

To access it, click the link in my bio 🙏🏻

Matt we enter 2022 with energy, optimism, and alignment. Or whatever energy in your system is true.

Big love ❤️
Cory
